Global setup:

 Download and install Git
  git config --global user.name "Your Name"
  git config --global user.email fabianosoriani@gmail.com


Next steps:

  mkdir javascriptinmotion
  cd javascriptinmotion
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:flockonus/javascriptinmotion.git
  git push origin master


Existing Git Repo?

  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:flockonus/javascriptinmotion.git
  git push origin master

